The year is 2003 and I am playing NFS Underground in our small condo in Bulgaria. Modifying cars and just dreaming. 20 years later I am living the dream. Blessed 🙏🏻 

#supra

Its ALIVE! After 2 Long months of dealing with terrible service from local shop. My ECU flew to Femto 🇫🇮 and got back to me just in 8days. Shoutout to @europerformancecenter for hitting me up and taking care of it. #supra #femto #b58

It’s been long 2weeks. Dealing with so many issues. Shitty job done by previous shop. Looking for hardware last min. Flashing that XHP was a pain 🤯. But the car is now back on the road and even on low boost it feels like a different animal. Now it’s time for data logs and more boost 📈
